# Pomodoro, Reminders & Growth

## State Expression (MVP)

Pet states use **CSS animation + bubbles** on the single `pet.png` asset — no per-state pose images.

## Pomodoro Defaults

- Focus: 25 min | Break: 5 min (user-configurable)
- Controls: start, pause, end
- On start: pet → `focus` animation
- On complete: +10 XP, pet → `happy` animation, encouragement bubble, log FocusSession

## User Settings

focusDuration, breakDuration, autoNextRound, soundAlert, petAnimationAlert

## Sedentary Reminder

- Default: every 60 min; options 30/45/60/90
- Pet → `remind` + bounce + bubble
- User confirms rest → happy feedback, reset timer
- Skipping repeatedly → `angry` state (brief)

## Growth Display

Name, level, XP bar, today focus count, streak days, last interaction time.

## Integration

- XP changes persist immediately
- Pomodoro panel: right-click「开始专注」or dedicated panel
- Stats feed growth page; no separate gamification framework in MVP

## Out of Scope

Decor unlocks, voice lines, cloud leaderboards — post-MVP hooks only.
